Scenario by Daisy | Artwork by Cinamon Games

You've been living in a miserable life after marrying your first love. One day, you get hit by a meteor shower and your're suddenly 18 years old again. In this most brilliant chapter of your life, you get another shot at choosing your first love. Who will it be? The man you passionately loved or the man who'll become a CEO in the future?
